      <title>工党的太阳能计划可能达不到关键气候目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/labour-s-solar-power-plan-may-fall-short-of-key-climate-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默的工党宣言承诺在下届议会结束前将太阳能发电能力提高两倍，但这可能不足以实现到 2050 年实现净零排放这一已经颇具挑战性的气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/labour-s-solar-power-plan-may-fall-short-of-key-climate-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
